Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:36.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the laundry, the towels\Nare in the upper right drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:42.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the washed towels\Nin the bottom drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:50.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take out the kitchen garbage on\NTuesday and Thursday by 8:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, it may not be taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:02:01.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wrap leftovers in plastic wrap\Nand put them in the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Period...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That about covers it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:13.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku and Toshiro will make\Na mess of things if they're left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm giving you this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're wearing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:35.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll place a special spiritual membrane\Naround you that will prevent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone but us Arrancars\Nfrom detecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:47.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, you'll be able\Nto pass through objects at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear it and don't take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:54.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a twelve-hour reprieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:06.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, I'll allow you to\Nsay goodbye to only one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If that person realizes what you're doing,\NI will consider it a violation of my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your time limit is midnight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:21.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Settle everything by then and\Ngo to the place I told you to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:28.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget... You can only\Nsay goodbye to one person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:03.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's enough!\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:10.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tightening\Nmy bandages too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't choke me.\N Good job, Ururu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Make him pass out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:21.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikkaku! Crap!\NLet go of Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay still, Ayasegawa!\N Let go, let go, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't move, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:40.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, oh dear, Lirin,\Nyou mustn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:45.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika is injured. You must be\Nmore gentle when you restrain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:50.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault for not listening to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yumichika all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:54.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such irresponsible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rewrap your bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're noisy wherever they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kisuke Urahara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a mysterious man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:38.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's been thinking about something ever\Nsince the Arrancars disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:45.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were lucky that this is\Nall that we suffered{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after all those Espada attacked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We underestimated them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're already prepared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've got to hurry\Nour battle preparations...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how quickly can we\Nget completely prepared?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get in touch\Nwith Soul Society?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:16.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, I seemed to have\Nbumped into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you bump into here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:51.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it felt kind of squishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:12.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only Arrancars will be\Nable to detect you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:24.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the same time, you'll be able to\Npass through objects at will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mizuiro, quickly, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,, Umm...\N If you don't hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop singing\Nthat song, Keigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, don't talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:11.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot something... Hey Hey!\NForgot something... Hey Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please cut that out,\NMr. Asano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:18.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah!\NThey can't see me right now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:22.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...\NStop being formal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I understand, Mr. Asano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:31.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's this chair on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ichigo come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone probably bumped into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's strange that\NChad, Inoue, Kuchiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and, for some reason,\NIshida all took off from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Could it be that they're\Ndoing something fun together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:00.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We really are being left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:01.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't group me in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:12.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may not be the only ones\Nwho have been left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Umm... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arisawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:42.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We may not be the only ones\Nwho have been left out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:44.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For example...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arisawa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Don't dawdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!\N Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you kicking?\NGo get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arisawa!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:47.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:03.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget... You can only\Nsay goodbye to one person. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't contact Inoue\Nin Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's\NSpiritual Wave interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the best I can do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:08.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My techniques don't heal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:10.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're actually a form\Nof spatial regression.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to activate\Nmy techniques,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:19.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to specify exactly\Nwhat I want to regress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now,\NIchigo's wound has{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:30.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arrancar Spiritual Pressure mixed in\Nwith his own Spiritual Pressure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:35.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With him in this state,\Nthis is the best I can regress it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:41.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get him out of this condition\Nas quickly as possible,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:44.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we need to get as far away\Nfrom him as we can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since we have Spiritual Pressure\Nthat is similar to that of Hollows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:52.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take him home and\Nlet him get some rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is the best treatment\Nfor him right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay... I understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:10.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo... Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:17.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of power...\Nare you trying to obtain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the Arrancars stop fighting\Nhalfway through and leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of things\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:34.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Anyway,\NI'll stop by Inoue's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother needs rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But Karin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He might wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:44.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we eat dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Please do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ichigo will be pleased...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:02.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made some for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it look delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... But I actually\Nneed to get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:18.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not hungr-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:25.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Rukia, you are hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, well... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you made it,\NI guess I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thank you, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Karin!\NBring the tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:41.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's been\Nsleeping all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:12.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. Getting beaten up\Nby students from a different school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still got a long way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened because\NI got tangled up with delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad that you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,, Whoa! What a waste...\N Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:41.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold tonight. If you're going out,\Nbe careful not to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:43.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:32.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,\NI wanted to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:10.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to Tatsuki, Sado, Ishida, Kuchiki,\Nand many other people, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:37.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Yuzu and Karin\Nate dinner here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose they'd want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:43.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They were sad that you\Nweren't around for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to eat dinner\Nwith you in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUSH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki's...room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:02.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, this is the first time\NI've come to Kurosaki's room alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It smells like him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:58.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good... I'm doing this\Neven though it's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:10.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, I had a lot of things\Nthat I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become\Na schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:16.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become\Nan astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:18.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be\Na cake maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go to a doughnut shop\Nthat had all kinds of doughnuts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and say I wanted everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wanted to go\Nto an ice cream shop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and say that I wanted everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had five lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be born in\Na different town each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd fill my stomach with\Ndifferent things each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have a different job\Neach time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And each time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:21:00.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd fall in love with\Nthe same person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:16.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I'm not getting through.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:24.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Soul Pager is too old.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is a new one that won't break\Neven if an elephant were to step on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But its design is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:30.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you for not being\Nable to realize how great it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does yours get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:33.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's out of range!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't brag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:36.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,, Illustrated guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,\N Hey, listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:41.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, there were\Nhuge noises in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:45.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Ikkaku and the others\Nfighting again, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:46.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:49.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:51.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}001 IKKAKU
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A spy with a license to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:53.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:56.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the attendant of\Na former shogun who fights evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.42,0:23:59.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be your brother in law.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,